The paper discusses the allocation policies and market decisions of a supplier in a forward market for rate-constrained energy services. This involves optimization and control problems, which are typically studied in the fields of game theory (cs.GT), machine learning (cs.LG), control systems (cs.SY), computational engineering (cs.CE), and software engineering (cs.SE). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
